This is a complete setup guide to get you started with my config and settings and has been requested by many fans. This will also show you how to save your settings and load them in the game. Down below is all the material you will need for this guide!

_______________________________________________

● Use Launch Options:
-novid -console -tickrate 128 +exec name.cfg

_______________________________________________

● My config
Config: http://pastebin.com/raw/dRvyvAW7
Config + Detailed Info: http://bananagaming.tv/configs

If you think the hud is too close to the center use:
safezonex 1 instead of 0.85
safezoney 1 instead of 0.85
_______________________________________________

● Crash'z Crosshair Map
https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=308490450

_______________________________________________

● If you have more than 1 folder in your Userdata folder:
-Go to this website: https://steamid.xyz
-Copy & Paste your Steam Community Profile
-Look at "Steam32 ID" to get your ID.

_______________________________________________

